tika.dc.description: Stop reading books by pretenders. Read this one and you will learn from an entrepreneur who created a seven-figure internet business from scratch. Matthew Paulson, Founder of Analyst Ratings Network, Lightning Releases and GoGo Photo Contest, has weathered the failures and triumphs of being an entrepreneur for nearly a decade. 40 Rules for Internet Business Success is his collection of core principles and strategies he used to grow his business.
